tursodatabase/limbo.summary: Recent activities in the limbo repository include the addition of support for uncorrelated subqueries and the introduction of a Remainder vdbe opcode. Furthermore, compatibility tests for the mod operator have been added and the COMPAT.md file has been updated. A pull request has also been submitted to add a guide on how to start contributing SQL functions, aiming to simplify the contribution process for new contributors.
